    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/6cfc85ad0bcdf258282aa151aee086e2.poster.avif?t=1737373356\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/6cfc85ad0bcdf258282aa151aee086e2.webm?t=1737373356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/6cfc85ad0bcdf258282aa151aee086e2.mp4?t=1737373356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>收集毁灭性强化道具，释放混沌伤害你的对手以夺得王冠！</strong><br><br>当你处于<strong>无敌状态</strong>时，可<strong>碰撞</strong>你的对手或者<strong>逃跑</strong>！<br><br>通过运用<strong>技能移动和强化道具</strong>的组合来骗过你的对手，在<strong>特殊关卡中</strong>抵达<strong>王冠</strong>！<br><br>闪避<strong>致命激光</strong>和危险的悬崖，保持在游戏中——<strong>快速反应</strong>是获胜的关键！<br><br>注意你碰了哪个<strong>按钮</strong>——有些会带来<strong>惊喜</strong>，而有些则可能毁掉你的胜利！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/9f5d907a15939f62d7809d7e15c5245c.poster.avif?t=1737373356\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/9f5d907a15939f62d7809d7e15c5245c.webm?t=1737373356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/9f5d907a15939f62d7809d7e15c5245c.mp4?t=1737373356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>与<strong>朋友</strong>或<strong>AI对手</strong>在最多<strong>4人</strong>的 <strong>惊险混乱的PVP战斗</strong> 中挑战<br></li><li><strong>释放</strong>一系列爆炸性的强化道具，包括<strong>炸弹、火箭、地雷和炮塔</strong><br></li><li><strong>变得更小、更快和隐形</strong>以躲避你的对手或攻击它们<br></li><li><strong>当你发出黄色光芒时</strong>攻击你的敌人，当他们占上风时<strong>躲避</strong>他们的进攻<br></li><li>在一些<strong>特殊关卡</strong>中到达<strong>王冠</strong>即可<strong>立即赢得</strong>该回合<br></li><li>禁用武器强化并在<strong>安宁的游戏模式</strong>中向朋友发起挑战<br></li><li>有<strong>60个独特的关卡</strong>，带有爆炸性的<strong>惊喜</strong>、<strong>激光</strong>、<strong>按钮</strong>和<strong>炸弹</strong><br></li><li><strong>基于物理的移动</strong>，注意不要掉下去！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/c0014132231f436fb0b7e2017ce824a0.poster.avif?t=1737373356\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/c0014132231f436fb0b7e2017ce824a0.webm?t=1737373356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/c0014132231f436fb0b7e2017ce824a0.mp4?t=1737373356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>注意：如果您在游戏中遇到控制器问题，请在Steam大图模式中禁用所有控制器。</strong>",
